Pauline Bush (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pauline_Bush_(actress) 0 Pauline Elvira Bush (May 22, 1886 – November 1, 1969) was an American silent film actress. She was nicknamed "The Madonna of the Movies". Pauline_Elvira_Bush ( May_22_,_1886 – November_1_,_1969 ) was an_American_silent_film_actress . She was_nicknamed " The_Madonna of the_Movies " .
